  "description": "This cluster of papers explores the anthropology of globalization, neoliberal governmentality, and cultural critique. It delves into the spatialities of states, structural violence, and the impact of colonialism on religious life. The papers also discuss the effects of neoliberalism on various cultures and societies, emphasizing the importance of ethnography in understanding these phenomena.",
